Explanation:Function longest_suffix_prefix_match:This function finds the longest suffix of prefixString that matches the beginning of text and the longest prefix of suffixString that matches the end of text.It iterates over possible suffixes and prefixes to find the longest matching segments.Function calculateScore:This function iterates over all possible substrings of text.For each substring, it calculates the prefix and suffix scores using longest_suffix_prefix_match.It keeps track of the substring with the highest combined prefix and suffix scores.In case of a tie, it returns the lexicographically smaller substring.
